        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrocracking reaction",
        "description": "在纯H₂气氛下，使用Pt/USY和PtRe/USY催化剂对正十六烷（C₁₆）进行加氢裂化，研究其活性和产物分布。",
        "text_snippet": "The hydrocracking of n-hexadecane (C₁₆, TCI, >98%) was carried out in the temperature range of 493–583K under a total pressure of 5MPa.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢裂化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrocracking reaction",
        "description": "在H₂O/H₂、CO/H₂或H₂O/CO/H₂混合气氛下，对正十六烷（C₁₆）进行加氢裂化，研究H₂O和CO对Pt/USY和PtRe/USY催化剂性能的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "Hydrocracking of C₁₆ in the presence of H₂O, CO, or H₂O/CO was also carried out in a similar manner, except for the co-injection of H₂O (15wt% of C₁₆), CO (4.3wt% of C₁₆), and H₂O/CO (15wt%/4.3wt% of C₁₆) into the 5MPa H₂, respectively.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 3,
        "reaction_type": "加氢转化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroconversion reaction",
        "description": "在单一反应器中，使用Pt/USY和PtRe/USY催化剂，对棕榈油进行一步法加氢转化（包括加氢、脱氧和加氢裂化级联反应）生产生物航煤。",
        "text_snippet": "The single-step hydroconversion of palm oil (Sigma-Aldrich, analytical standard) was carried out similarly over 1.2g of the sieved catalysts in the temperature range of 523–573K under a total pressure of 5MPa.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
